high_descs: Walk forward and turn right into the other room, walk forward toward the armchair with the newspaper on it, then turn right and go to the TV.
Pick up the newspaper which is on the TV stand, behind the remote.
Turn around and walk across the room to the green sofa.
Put the newspaper on the sofa, in front of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move a newspaper from a TV stand to a sofa.

high_descs: Move to the left side of the TV stand to the right of the green bin
Pick up the newspaper on top of the TV stand on the far left side
Carry the newspaper to the large sofa in the corner of the room
Place the newspaper on top of the left side of the sofa in front of the laptop
anns.task_desc: Carry a newspaper to the sofa

high_descs: Walk into the living room and over to the TV stand
Pick up the newspaper behind the remote on the TV stand
Turn around and walk over to the sofa
Set the newspaper down on the sofa in front of the laptop
anns.task_desc: Put the newspaper on the sofa

high_descs: Walk to the window in front of you, then turn right and pass through the doorway. Walk forward to the chair in the corner, turn right and walk to the coffee table. Then turn left and walk to the left corner of the entertainment center.
Pick up the newspaper from the entertainment center.
Turn around and walk to the couch.
Place the newspaper on the front of the couch next to the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Move the newspaper from the entertainment center to the couch.

high_descs: Turn right and then go straight. Veer right to the TV stand.
Pick up the newspaper behind the remote.
Turn around and walk to the couch.
Put the newspaper on the couch on the side of the laptop.
anns.task_desc: Put a newspaper on a couch.
